			<cite>

<span class="count">13</span>

<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c6dbe265dbb2eeb5d7a7f9af967810fd?s=40&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />
